General.Name: Tomer Energy Royalties (2012) Ltd
General.Description: Delek Royalties (2012) Ltd., a special-purpose yield company, holds the right to receive overriding royalties in respect of oil and/or gas and/or other valuable materials derived from the shares of various oil and gas companies and entities in Israel. It holds rights to receive royalties from the Tamar Reservoir and Daliyat projects in Israel. The company was founded in 2012 and is based in Herzliya, Israel.
